column5: On Simcoe yet ? Seen a few boats out  , mine one of them but nothing to write home about  .
I've been out 3 times and caught as many perch as I wanted each time. I was out there 3 weeks ago pounding them.... lol .  S.
The last time I was on Simcoe I was nailing lakers one after the other...Just before the ice started to break away from shore...
did you get a free PFD Mike?
How many fow Sinker , but you were'nt in Simcoe tho ........
the perch have been going good on simcoe for about 3 weeks on and off in the boat and also off shore.Some days have been very good and some so so.
True dat   I was in the boat on one of those days
True Dat too   Been perching open water with this silly bugger on Simcoe since March 18th
They been hammering the Perch all weekend
Actually, no, I'm not at all.      They're out there, you just gotta find 'em! Shallow, shallow, shallow....  S.
